            <img src="/images/sterling-portrait.png" alt="Sterling Cooley" class="about-hero-img">
            <div class="about-hero-copy">
                <p>Founded by Sterling Cooley, VagusHub helps people understand and improve vagus nerve function through evidence-based methods like breathing, movement, electrical VNS, and emerging ultrasound techniques.</p>
                <div class="hero-links">
                    <a class="btn primary" href="/getting-started">Start Here: Getting Started</a>
                    <a class="btn outline" href="/media">Watch Interviews & Media</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
        <div class="mission">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At VagusHub, we're dedicated to helping people understand and optimize their vagus nerve function for better health, reduced stress, and improved well-being.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="story">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded by health enthusiasts and nervous system experts, VagusHub emerged from a passion for helping others achieve optimal health through natural means.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise">
            <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
            <p>We combine traditional wisdom with modern science to provide you with the most effective techniques for vagus nerve stimulation and regulation.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-links">
        <h2>Featured Guides</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <a class="feature-card" href="/getting-started">
                <h3>Getting Started with VNS</h3>
                <p>Beginner-friendly on-ramps, breathing, and first-week practices.</p>
            </a>
            <a class="feature-card" href="/ultrasound">
                <h3>Ultrasound VNS</h3>
                <p>Learn foundations, safety, and protocols for ultrasound stimulation.</p>
            </a>
            <a class="feature-card" href="/benefits">
                <h3>Benefits of VNS</h3>
                <p>Explore the science-backed advantages reported by users and studies.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline">
        <h2>About Sterling Cooley — Timeline</h2>
        <ol class="timeline-list">
            <li>
                <div class="date">2013</div>
                <div class="desc">Begins ultrasound engineering research in Berkeley, CA.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2014</div>
                <div class="desc">Hired by University of Arizona (Tucson) and Dr. Stuart Hameroff to develop ultrasound hardware for neural and consciousness stimulation research.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2015</div>
                <div class="desc">Raises VC funding; moves to Shenzhen, China to accelerate device development.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2016</div>
                <div class="desc">Relocates to Washington, DC; coordinates ultrasound grant funding with NIH. During a DARPA/Pentagon meeting, hears interest in Vagus Nerve Stimulation.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2017</div>
                <div class="desc">Begins experimentation with ultrasound stimulation of the cervical (neck) vagus nerve; finds exceptional effects.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2018</div>
                <div class="desc">Launches human trial with 50 initial participants for ultrasound VNS therapy — a major success.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2019</div>
                <div class="desc">Launches an online course with human coaching add-on; supports 300+ participants rapidly and successfully.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2020</div>
                <div class="desc">Vagus Nerve Stimulation & Repair Program and Facebook group grow to tens of thousands of daily readers and ultrasound users.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2021</div>
                <div class="desc">Trains additional coaches to implement ultrasound VNS into their successful practices.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2022</div>
                <div class="desc">Presents at the 5th Annual Bioelectrical Medicine Conference (NYC); deepens insights into the Insular Cortex–Vagus connection.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2023</div>
                <div class="desc">Develops a Brain & Vagus Nerve protocol with faster, greater results for clients.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2024</div>
                <div class="desc">Transitions training fully online via “Ultra Skool”; expands research into ultrasound and neurodegeneration; launches an Alzheimer’s Research Group.</div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="date">2025</div>
                <div class="desc">Leads mid-scale human study applying ultrasound to treat and potentially reverse Alzheimer’s disease; receives IRB & FDA nod to continue.</div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <div class="timeline-cta">
            <a class="btn outline" href="/media">See interviews and talks along this journey →</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

